{% extends "layout.njk" %}
{% block content %}
  <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Welcome</h1>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    This is an internal demo to explore the feasibility of a case management system with a chat interface. The agentic AI can create, read, update, and delete entities, and orchestrate these tools according to business logic.
  </p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>
      <a class="govuk-link" href="/cases">Create a case manually on the Cases page</a> and append notes to it.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="govuk-link" href="/chat">Move to the Chat window</a> and ask the agent to create, update, or delete cases and notes for you.
    </li>
    <li>
      You can always return to the <a class="govuk-link" href="/cases">Cases page</a> to see the current list of cases and their notes.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    This demo is for exploration purposes only. Do not include PII. Do not include live data.
  </p>
{% endblock %}
